<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Erwirdig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Fricze<ex>n</ex></expan> von Mayental und des
                                <expan>Weissemburg<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief wol
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> und <expan>lasse<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> erwirdikeit wissen, daz uns das
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> getrewlich leid ist. Nu geviel uns wol, ob ew
                        das güt dewchte, daz ir dann <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>hochg<ex>eporn</ex></expan>
<expan>fürst<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>burgg<ex>ra</ex>fen</expan> Johansen darumb
                            <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> het, des
                            <expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> Fricz <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        Mayental ist, und so <expan>wolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir im darumb
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> auch <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>
<expan>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> brief
                        mit <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> schicken. Und künden wir iht gütes darczü
                        getün, das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> czemal <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>. Wan wo
                        wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erwirdik<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb und dienst
                            <expan>beweise<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>möht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                <expan>allcz<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>.</ab>
